Section.name: About GKCE
Section.description:
Gokula Krishna College of Engineering (GKCE), Nellore was established in 2001. The college is sponsored by Sri Krishna Educational Society and is known for its standard technical education and associated research. The college was awarded ISO 9001:2000 certificate by JAS-ANZ of Australia and New Zealand, the first education institute among the nearby engineering colleges and first in the district and is a member of ISTE.
